SEARCH
Module photos60
Package photos

Class SearchPhotos

java.lang.Object
photos.SearchPhotos
public class SearchPhotos extends Object
Utility class for searching photos based on various criteria. Supports date range searches, tag-based searches, and conjunctions/disjunctions.
Author:
Group 60

      public static List<Photo> searchByTagsAnd(List<Photo> photos, List<Tag> tags)
      Searches for photos with multiple tags using AND logic. A photo must have all specified tags to be included.
      Parameters:
      photos - the list of photos to search
      tags - the list of tags (tag type-value pairs)
      Returns:
      a list of photos with all specified tags

    • searchByTagsOr

      public static List<Photo> searchByTagsOr(List<Photo> photos, List<Tag> tags)
      Searches for photos with multiple tags using OR logic. A photo must have at least one of the specified tags to be included.
      Parameters:
      photos - the list of photos to search
      tags - the list of tags (tag type-value pairs)
      Returns:
      a list of photos with at least one of the specified tags
